# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:13
translate chinese jamietv2_fd039b16:

    # "I walk up to Jamie's door and knock."
    "我走到杰米的门前敲了敲门。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:14
translate chinese jamietv2_fdad75c4:

    # "I wait a bit for her to answer and after a few moments, I almost walk away thinking that she isn't home or is busy or something."
    "我等了一会儿她开门，过了一会儿，我几乎就要走开了，以为她不在家或者很忙之类的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:19
translate chinese jamietv2_56b288a0:

    # "Then, just when I am about to leave, she opens the door."
    "就在我正要离开的时候，她打开了门。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:20
translate chinese jamietv2_348b659c:

    # gnd "Hey sorry, I must have fell asleep on the couch."
    gnd "嘿，抱歉，我大概是在沙发上睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:21
translate chinese jamietv2_85e15039:

    # pc "Oh I'm sorry, I didn't mean to wake you. Was just wondering if you wanted to hang out?"
    pc "哦，对不起，我不是故意吵醒你的。只是想问问你愿不愿意一起出去玩？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:22
translate chinese jamietv2_8cddc873:

    # gnd "Sure, want to come watch TV with me?"
    gnd "当然，要不要来和我一起看电视？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:23
translate chinese jamietv2_6eafa1e5:

    # pc "Are you sure? You look pretty tired."
    pc "你确定吗？你看起来挺累的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:24
translate chinese jamietv2_d5f53ad3:

    # gnd "I'm exhausted, but I'd still like to spend some time with you."
    gnd "我确实累坏了，但还是想和你待会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:25
translate chinese jamietv2_35743d5e:

    # pc "Okay then."
    pc "那好吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:26
translate chinese jamietv2_d6443097:

    # "We walk inside and sit down on her couch to watch TV together."
    "我们走进屋里，坐在她的沙发上一起看电视。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:29
translate chinese jamietv2_4eefcd41:

    # pc "You not been sleeping well?"
    pc "你最近没睡好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:30
translate chinese jamietv2_d3a1e5f8:

    # gnd "I've just been studying a lot. It's been tough."
    gnd "我最近一直在学习，挺辛苦的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:31
translate chinese jamietv2_6d7e76b4:

    # pc "Tell me about it."
    pc "我懂。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:32
translate chinese jamietv2_56872787:

    # gnd "But I'm glad to spend some time with you, even if I'm sleepy."
    gnd "不过能和你待会儿，就算我困得要命也值得。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:37
translate chinese jamietv2_c7a75159:

    # gnd "Are you implying I'm not cute when I'm not sleepy?"
    gnd "你是说我没睡着的时候就不可爱了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:38
translate chinese jamietv2_4db958a5:

    # pc "What? No."
    pc "什么？才不是呢。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:39
translate chinese jamietv2_cf0825c6:

    # gnd "I'm just kidding. Thanks, you're sweet."
    gnd "我只是开玩笑。谢谢，你真贴心。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:42
translate chinese jamietv2_175d3768:

    # gnd "What? Are you serious?"
    gnd "什么？你是认真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:43
translate chinese jamietv2_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:44
translate chinese jamietv2_f3a7bdd3:

    # gnd "That's probably not a good idea. My dad might actually kill you."
    gnd "这恐怕不是个好主意。我爸说不定真会杀了你。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:45
translate chinese jamietv2_796397b3:

    # pc "It might be worth the risk."
    pc "冒这个险或许值得。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:46
translate chinese jamietv2_34f266ea:

    # gnd "You're crazy!"
    gnd "你疯了！"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:49
translate chinese jamietv2_d13864ee:

    # gnd "But no, let's just watch TV."
    gnd "不过算了，咱们还是看电视吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:52
translate chinese jamietv2_8105064d:

    # "She smiles at me and we both turn towards the TV and watch the show."
    "她冲我笑了笑，我们俩一起转过身，看着电视节目。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:55
translate chinese jamietv2_e4b4fe92:

    # "After the first commercial break, I hear her snoring softly and a moment later, she leans over and lays her head on my shoulder."
    "第一个广告插播结束后，我听到她轻轻打起了鼾，片刻之后，她侧过身，把头靠在我的肩膀上。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:56
translate chinese jamietv2_72d126bc:

    # "I sit there like that, feeling her warm weight against me, smelling the scent of her shampoo. It's nice."
    "我就那样坐着，感受着她温暖的身体压在我身上，闻着她洗发水的香味。真舒服。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:57
translate chinese jamietv2_a7276863:

    # "I watch the rest of the show, letting her sleep on my shoulder until the credits roll."
    "我看着剩下的节目，任由她在我肩头睡到片尾字幕滚动。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:60
translate chinese jamietv2_aced7ae5:

    # "The music playing during the credits wakes her and she opens her eyes and looks up at me, putting her hand on my chest."
    "片尾曲的旋律把她唤醒，她睁开眼睛抬头看着我，把手搭在我的胸口。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:61
translate chinese jamietv2_222fe902:

    # gnd "Oh man, I missed the whole thing."
    gnd "天啊，我整集都没看到。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:62
translate chinese jamietv2_7289beae:

    # pc "Yeah, I'll have to fill you in later."
    pc "是啊，等会儿我得给你补讲一下。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:63
translate chinese jamietv2_d912edc5:

    # gnd "You could have woke me up."
    gnd "你明明可以叫醒我的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:66
translate chinese jamietv2_fd8175bb:

    # gnd "I definitely did."
    gnd "我确实叫了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:68
translate chinese jamietv2_7b910158:

    # gnd "You're so silly."
    gnd "你真傻。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:69
translate chinese jamietv2_d404c590:

    # gnd "Do you really think I'm cute?"
    gnd "你真的觉得我很可爱吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:70
translate chinese jamietv2_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:71
translate chinese jamietv2_d2d7ae9c:

    # gnd "I think you're cute too."
    gnd "我也觉得你很可爱。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:72
translate chinese jamietv2_e8e9a7f7:

    # "Once again, her dad picks the worst moment to open the door and walk in."
    "她爸爸又挑了个最糟糕的时机开门走了进来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:73
translate chinese jamietv2_9da07a83:

    # "Jamie leans away from me and stands up."
    "杰米从我身边挪开，站了起来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:79
translate chinese jamietv2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_011.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_011.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:80
translate chinese jamietv2_25b98dfa:

    # gnd "Hey, Daddy."
    gnd "嗨，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:81
translate chinese jamietv2_20dcad47:

    # jd "Send him home."
    jd "让他回家吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:82
translate chinese jamietv2_f2596c67:

    # "Her dad doesn't say anything else and instead walks past us and into the kitchen."
    "她爸爸没再说什么，径直从我们身边走过，进了厨房。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:86
translate chinese jamietv2_84d4365c:

    # gnd "He must have had a bad day."
    gnd "他今天肯定过得很糟糕。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:87
translate chinese jamietv2_b44cf649:

    # pc "I should probably go."
    pc "我大概该走了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:88
translate chinese jamietv2_a6870bf2:

    # gnd "Yeah, I'm sorry."
    gnd "嗯，对不起。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:89
translate chinese jamietv2_b219d344:

    # pc "It's okay."
    pc "没关系。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:92
translate chinese jamietv2_36b8ae4f:

    # gnd "Thanks for coming over tonight. I had a good time."
    gnd "谢谢你今晚过来。我玩得很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:93
translate chinese jamietv2_041dfd87:

    # pc "More like you had a good nap."
    pc "倒不如说你睡了个好觉。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:94
translate chinese jamietv2_b762e00f:

    # gnd "That too. Your shoulder is very comfy."
    gnd "也是。你的肩膀很舒服。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:98
translate chinese jamietv2_4bbcc4b9:

    # gnd "I might take you up on that."
    gnd "我可能会接受你的提议。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:100
translate chinese jamietv2_f9097bdf:

    # gnd "I'm sure they'll show re-runs all week."
    gnd "我敢肯定这周都会重播。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:101
translate chinese jamietv2_dfc3c586:

    # pc "Alright, well I better head home."
    pc "好吧，那我还是回家吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:103
translate chinese jamietv2_ecb1e778:

    # gnd "Okay, [pcname]. See you again soon."
    gnd "好的，[pcname]。很快再见。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:104
translate chinese jamietv2_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "再见。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:105
translate chinese jamietv2_1557defd:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "说完，她回屋去了，我则走回自己家。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:2
