    new "第一次和她一起看电视的几天后，"

    # game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:3
    old "go to her house on a weekday evening and watch TV again."
    new "在一个工作日的晚上，你又去她家看电视。"

    # game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:34
    old "I'm glad too."
    new "我也很高兴。"

    # game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:36
